VHow did this happen?
p42
aVWell, we're no genetically hardier than our ancestors were 10,000 years ago.
p43
aVThis increase in life expectancy is the remarkable product of culture \u2014
p44
aVthe crucible that holds science and technology
p45
aVand wide-scale changes in behavior that improve health and well-being.
p46
aVThrough cultural changes, our ancestors largely eliminated early death
p47
aVso that people can now live out their full lives.
