VNow there are problems associated with aging \u2014
p50
aVdiseases, poverty, loss of social status.
p51
aVIt's hardly time to rest on our laurels.
p52
aVBut the more we learn about aging,
p53
aVthe clearer it becomes that a sweeping downward course
p54
aVis grossly inaccurate.
p55
aVAging brings some rather remarkable improvements \u2014
p56
aVincreased knowledge, expertise \u2014
